USishi usho lokhu emuva kokuxoshwa konogada abawu-14 abalahlwe yicala lokuzama ukweba amatekisi (Toyota Quantums) akwaPrasa ngo-Okthoba 31 wonyaka odlule. Kuthiwa labo nogada bagasela emahhovisi akwaPrasa ngabo 1:30 kuya ku-1:50 bafike bakhomba ngezibhamu onogada ababesebenza ngalolo suku, babashaya, babavala amehlo baze bababopha nezandla. Ngebhadi balahlwa elakubo njengoba bathi besahlela ukuhamba namatekisi kwagasela amaphoyisa baboshwa. Labo nogada baqondiswa ubugwegwe icala labalahla. USishi uthe kuyathusa ukuthi onogada abawu-14 bazama ukweba amatekisi baze balimaza ozakwabo. â€œKuyathusa ukuthi banikwe umsebenzi wokuvikela umphakathi nempahla kodwa yibona abazama ukuyeba."."USihlalo weBhodi lakwaPrasa uNkk Khanyisile Kweyama naye usishayele ihlombe isinqumo sokuxoshwa kwalabo nogada.